Name: Fenan Klein Afrika

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
Review Text: Absolutely loved the food and specials beers, this time was the Mango beer! We had a big plate to share in 3 and we almost couldn't finish it as big as it was. :) Definitely recommend and good prices.

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
Review Text: Delicious food and cheap too. I don't give 5 stars since they do not accept credit card and it is not clearly written outside.

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
Review Text: The reviews really do not lie, this place is the best Ethiopian in Amsterdam! I usually order the lentils which are delicious and so flavouful. I'd highly recommend for anybody looking to try a new cuisine or satisfy that urge to eat Ethiopian food. They also have a hard to find imported Ethiopian beer that's delicious!

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
Review Text: Probably one of my favorite restaurants in Amsterdam. Every bite is extremely delicious and tasty. I have tried other Ethiopian places, but this one for me has the best flavor. Customer service is also very friendly, i highly recommend it :)

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
Review Text: The best Ethiopian food in Amsterdam. The restaurant is very small, but that doesn't distract from the amazing and quality food. Even though the food is delicious and the portion sizes decent, it's still excellent value for money. Pro tip: if they have the Ethiopian beer available, order it!

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika

Review Text: So traditional, food delicious, good prices. I hardly recommend the place. But I really enjoyed this place, and if you are looking for  another experience you should try.

Name: Fenan Klein Afrika
